<runspec version="MOVES5.0.1">
	<description><![CDATA[NOx speciation products (NO, NO2, HONO) running exhaust — exercises NOCalculator and NO2Calculator.

Requests the NOx product pollutants (Nitrogen Oxide 32, Nitrogen Dioxide 33,
Nitrous Acid/HONO 34) for Running Exhaust (process 1). These are the output
pollutants that NOCalculator and NO2Calculator register for; the Phase 0
hot-path fixtures use total NOx (pollutant 3) which feeds the speciation
calculators but is not in their registration set.]]></description>
